{"tid":1442482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［裝備］請各位自備自備自備自備自備自備裝備","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:59:38.000Z","uid":6854,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d950ac9049420cc777662ca2ec01124bc1d9dbc","tid":1442482,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到琴日仲有好多人連基本眼罩都冇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家快閃行街 唔會好似以前定點勁大個物資站咁</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位物資跟身 基本裝備眼罩頭盔口罩都自備定</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好以為自己行唔前就唔洗帶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇人知狗會邊到走出嚟邊到放彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行得出街就隨時都會係前線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好老馮諗住出去拎裝備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出面裝備都要錢買 盡留俾前線用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有 咪撚扔裝 上次拎完要帶返出嚟用</span></span>"},{"pid":"20dee7bce2daae40b7a79ea0aa13212948d3f2cc","tid":1442482,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAS7oS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAS7oS1.jpg&h=055023d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27dcb29692c9f7209a217c5de5be7584fde20b0d","tid":1442482,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3nvmEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3nvmEM.jpg&h=489de5ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"822d0d30915fe090bf1d1f3d487b799300ce9351","tid":1442482,"uid":6854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img 